                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;14080  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14081  void watchdog_enable (void) 
0142b6  f04f4080          MOV      r0,#0x40000000
;;;14082  {
;;;14083  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;
0142ba  49fe              LDR      r1,|L1.83636|

;;;14084  LPC_WDT->WDCLKSEL=0;

0142c2  6101              STR      r1,[r0,#0x10]
;;;14085  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;

0142c8  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;14086  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
0142ca  f04f01aa          MOV      r1,#0xaa
0142ce  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14087  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
0142d0  f04f0155          MOV      r1,#0x55
0142d4  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14088  }
0142d6  4770              BX       lr
;;;14089  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;14090  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14091  void watchdog_reset (void) 
0142d8  f04f4080          MOV      r0,#0x40000000
;;;14092  {
;;;14093  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
0142dc  f04f01aa          MOV      r1,#0xaa
0142e0  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14094  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

0142e6  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14095  }
0142e8  4770              BX       lr
;;;14096  
                          ENDP

                  SysTick_Handler PROC
;;;14102  //***********************************************
;;;14103  void SysTick_Handler (void) 	 /* SysTick Interrupt Handler (1ms)    */

;;;14104  {
;;;14105  //sys_plazma++;
;;;14106  b2000Hz=1;

                  |L1.82700|
;;;14112  	}
;;;14113  
;;;14114  if(++t0cnt4>=2)
